# Competency question: "What language-proficiency levels does PURRDF model, and on
# which scales?" Expected: the ProficiencyLevel value individuals — the CEFR band
# (A1–C2) plus scale-free native/heritage — each tied to its scale by
# purrdf:levelScale. The leveled detail lives on the reified purrdf:LanguageProficiency.

PREFIX purrdf: <https://blackcatinformatics.ca/purrdf/>

SELECT ?level WHERE {
    ?level a purrdf:ProficiencyLevel .
}
ORDER BY ?level
